e of AIMS and provides caution as to the upper limits in parameter\nstep size. All tests demonstrate the flexibility and capability of AIMS as an\nanalysis tool and its potential to perform accurate ensemble analysis with\ncurrent and future asteroseismic data yields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jan 2019 10:33:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-17"}
