$, as well as weaker HeI lines. The spectral features, along with the\nstructure of the light curve, suggest that MASTER OT J061451.70-272535.5 is a\nnew magnetic cataclysmic variable, most likely of the synchronised Polar\nsubclass.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jan 2019 10:42:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-10"}
