enter distance to the back stress created by piled-up geometrically\nnecessary dislocations in the plastic zone and to the additional constraint\nimposed by the GB on the plastic zone size.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jan 2019 11:25:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-27"}
