}$ and fake\n$A^\\mathrm{CP;CPT}_{\\alpha\\beta}$ and $A^\\mathrm{T;CPT}_{\\alpha\\beta}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jan 2019 14:34:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Feb 2019 15:36:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-01"}
